lead_paragraph: Harry Redknapp came down to the earth with a bump in the second match of his cameo as an international manager on Tuesday when his Jordan side were thrashed 5-1 by Australia to almost certainly drop out of contention for the 2018 World Cup.

headline.print_headline: Redknapp's International Cameo Ends on a Low
headline.main: Redknapp's International Cameo Ends on a Low
